  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battles</h2>Immerse yourself in a world of endless battles and challenges. Infinity Castle Dungeon will give you the opportunity to test your mind and reaction, but be careful - the world of Infinity Castle Dungeon does not forgive mistakes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621440/extras/021f758ea03e61ec3981fb4aa721ebe7.poster.avif?t=1725608681\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621440/extras/021f758ea03e61ec3981fb4aa721ebe7.webm?t=1725608681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621440/extras/021f758ea03e61ec3981fb4aa721ebe7.mp4?t=1725608681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural Map Generation</h2>The castle in Infinity Castle Dungeon is not just walls, it is alive and only it knows what the next room will be in front of you. Don't forget to stock up on resources and luck and go to the unique world of Infinity Castle Dungeon.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621440/extras/ea897096a29a5ac6604de9c527f863da.poster.avif?t=1725608681\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621440/extras/ea897096a29a5ac6604de9c527f863da.webm?t=1725608681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621440/extras/ea897096a29a5ac6604de9c527f863da.mp4?t=1725608681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
